            <head>choice</head>
            <p>In the element <gi>choice</gi>, errors and their corrections can be marked up with <gi>sic</gi>, <gi>orig</gi>, and <gi>corr</gi>. All  
            can take <att>resp</att> to state the person who identified the marked up error and/or provided a correction. If <att>resp</att> is used only with <gi>choice</gi>, it 
            will be assumed that this statement is valid for all of its child elements.</p>
         </div>
